"title": "8335: reverence, and blessing",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8335",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Reverence for God brings favour to individual believers, their families and the community to which they belong.</p>\n<h2>God's blessing is conditional upon reverence for him</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps128:1\">PSA 128:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps115:1\">PSA 115:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl8:12\">ECC 8:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:39\">JER 32:39</a></p>\n<h2>The characteristics of reverence</h2>\n<h3>Wisdom is based on reverence for God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps111:10\">PSA 111:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:7\">PRO 1:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov9:10\">PRO 9:10</a></p>\n<h3>Reverence is pure and eternal</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:9\">PSA 19:9</a></p>\n<h3>Reverence will characterise the Messiah</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:2-Isa11:3\">ISA 11:2–11:3</a></p>\n<h2>God responds to those who revere him</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:11\">PSA 147:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:14\">PSA 25:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:16-Mal3:18\">MAL 3:16–3:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:35\">ACT 10:35</a></p>\n<h3>Reverence brings God's special attention and compassion</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh1:11\">NEH 1:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:18\">PSA 33:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:13\">PSA 103:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:17\">PSA 103:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:19\">PSA 145:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:50\">LUK 1:50</a></p>\n<h3>God is good to those who revere him</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:19\">PSA 31:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa33:6\">ISA 33:6</a></p>\n<h3>Reverence brings God's protection and deliverance</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:7\">PSA 34:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps60:4\">PSA 60:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps115:11\">PSA 115:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:26\">PRO 14:26</a></p>\n<h3>God meets the needs of those who revere him</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod1:21\">EXO 1:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:9\">PSA 34:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps111:5\">PSA 111:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:24-Jer5:25\">JER 5:24–5:25</a></p>\n<h2>Reverence for God is rewarded</h2>\n<h3>God rewards the reverent with prosperity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:24\">DEU 6:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:9\">JOB 1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:12-Ps25:13\">PSA 25:12–25:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps85:9\">PSA 85:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps112:1\">PSA 112:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps128:4\">PSA 128:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:4\">PRO 22:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal4:2\">MAL 4:2</a></p>\n<h3>Those who revere God avoid his judgment</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:58-Deut28:67\">DEU 28:58–28:67</a></p>\n<h3>God rewards reverence with long life and future hope</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:27\">PRO 10:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:27\">PRO 14:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:23\">PRO 19:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:17-Prov23:18\">PRO 23:17–23:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl8:13\">ECC 8:13</a></p>\n<h2>God's blessings on those who revere him are a witness to the nations</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer33:9\">JER 33:9</a></p>\n<h2>Reverence ensures success in leadership</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam23:3\">2SA 23:3</a> <em>David</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr26:5\">2CH 26:5</a> <em>Uzziah</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:31\">ACT 9:31</a></p>",
